    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Made in Hong Kong. By Unreal Engine 5.5.4. Map data from the Land Dept of the government of the HKSAR. (Open3Dhk)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Background:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kwun Tong is a short horror game that take place in an industrial district. People become soulless after economic collapse. Wandering on streets. Looking for money......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Game is about 60mins in length</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Challenging boss fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Minimal text and no document to read</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Based on actual geometry</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 1st POV</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Story with several chapters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Linear gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Settings:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Supports Full Screen / Windowed Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Supports TSR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Supports HDR</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- No save feature. You can access different chapters freely from main menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By Unreal Engine 5.5.4.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>一座被崩潰困擾的城市</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觀塘 | Kwun Tong 是一款短小的高端氛圍恐怖-冒險遊戲，設定在後崩潰的香港，迷茫的市民為了錢而徘徊。由虛幻引擎5.4.4建構，使用真實世界地圖數據，它提供了一種超現實的城市現實主義與實驗性恐怖的混合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>一個衰敗的城市景觀</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在觀塘中導航一個第一人稱，基於章節的故事，其中環境敘事和詭異的視覺效果取代了對話和傳統的闡述。在大約60分鐘的運行時間內，你必須探索荒廢的街道，面對具有挑戰性的Boss戰鬥，並慢慢揭開一個安靜絕望的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一個關鍵的限制是缺乏存檔系統——這是一個故意的設計選擇，強化了遊戲的無情氛圍，但可能會讓喜歡更靈活節奏的玩家感到沮喪。雖然章節選擇允許訪問遊戲的不同部分，但會話中的進度不會被保留，使其變得不那麼寬容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>對於實驗性恐怖的粉絲</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觀塘 | Kwun Tong 獎勵那些欣賞安靜、不安環境和非常規敘事的玩家。它的現實世界設定和簡約敘事風格使其成為恐怖類型中的獨特文化遺物。只需準備好它嚴格的無保存結構，這可以增強沉浸感——但以便利性為代價。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 重現一個真實的香港地區 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 講一個獨特的恐怖故事 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 提供激烈的Boss戰鬥</p>",
